name: Fvck Me Now
description:
Betty Fvck is a drag artist and performer from Helsinki who is fvcking amazing in front of the camera.  I told her "play with the skirt" and this is what happened.  She does her own makeup and hair and is absolutely stunning.  What a joy it was to create this skirt and headdress for her to model!  It was a cold winter night in Berlin, but my heart was warm with inspiration by the time she left my studio!

Model instagram.com/bettyfvck/
Photo, skirt and headdress by BubblesAndFrown.etsy.com
Vegan harness by instagram.com/tommyvowles/
